{"tid":2437043,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【維港滙I】發展商加推108伙 折實入場費約689萬 一半單位低過一千萬","createTime":"2021-03-07T15:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T15:17:48.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"31d17e217b6f04efb020adc6b4171702d7d11330","tid":2437043,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:09:29.000Z","msg":"【維港滙I】發展商加推108伙 折實入場費約689萬 一半單位低過一千萬<br />\n20:12 2021/03/07<br />\n<br />\n&quot;西南九龍GRAND VICTORIA I維港滙I今日加推2號價單，涉及108伙，新一批單位實用面積為277至835平方呎，主要集中於第3A、3B及5座，當中包括4個開放式單位、49個1房單位、45個2房戶、10個3房單位......扣除最高20%折扣率後，折實價為689.44萬至2,298.72萬元，折實呎價由22,335至28,396元。以折實價計，這批單位有53伙，即約49.1%低於1,000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n發展商表示，新一批單位輕微加價1%至2%......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2894719/%E3%80%90%E7%B6%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%BB%99I%E3%80%91%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%95%86%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A8108%E4%BC%99%20%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6%E5%85%A5%E5%A0%B4%E8%B2%BB%E7%B4%84689%E8%90%AC%20%20%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E4%BD%8E%E9%81%8E%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2894719%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BB%2599I%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258E%25A8108%25E4%25BC%2599%2520%25E6%258A%2598%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E7%25B4%2584689%25E8%2590%25AC%2520%2520%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E4%25BD%258E%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258D%2583%25E8%2590%25AC%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058hAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=aec9274a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2894719/%E3%80%90%E7%B6%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%BB%99I%E3%80%91%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%95%86%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A8108%E4%BC%99%20%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6%E5%85%A5%E5%A0%B4%E8%B2%BB%E7%B4%84689%E8%90%AC%20%20%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E4%BD%8E%E9%81%8E%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC?mtc=60037</a><br />\n